    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Walbrandus">Vualprandi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> ricevono da
                            <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia
                        Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>,
                        per cartula livellario nomine (…), una petia de terra quod est orto illo
                            <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Clusae/gates">foras <rs
                                key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista Lucense prope <rs
                                key="#Clusae/gates">porta Sancti Fridiani</rs></placeName>,
                        pertenentes ipsius <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70" key="#Confinia #Clusae/gates #Churches"
                            >Sancti Fridiani</orgName>, qui est de suppotestatem ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; et <rs key="#Confinia">est tenentes ambas
                            capitas</rs> in <rs>via publica</rs>, lato uno tenet in terra <persName
                            key="#Confinia"><name ref="Ildebertus">Ildiberti</name></persName>, et
                        alio lato tenet in terra quod est orto, qui fuit <persName key="#Confinia"
                            >quondam <name ref="Ermefredus">Ermifridi</name></persName>. Obblighi:
                        (…) suprascripta petia de terra quod est orto (…) in integrum nobis dedisti
                        tali ordinem ut da admodum in nostra vel de nostris heredibus sint
                        potestatem eas abendum, inperandum, laborare faciendum, gubernandum,
                        meliorandum et nobis eas privato nomine usufructuandum (…). Censo: pro omni
                        censum et iustitiam exinde tibi vel ad successoribus tuis ad pars ipsius
                        ecclesie Sancti Fridiani, per singulos annos, reddere debeamus ad
                        suprascripta ecclesia Sancti Fridiani, per omnem mense novembrio, argentum
                        denarios bonos expendivilis numero quatuor vobis vel ad ministarialem
                        vestro, quas in ipsa ecclesia pro tempore fuerit tantum (…). Pena:
                        spondeamus nos qui supra Petrus et Andreas, una cum nostris heredibus,
                        conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos decem (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Flaipertus"
                            >Flaipertus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Fridegausus">Fridicauso</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gausfredus">Cosfridi</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
